name: OPPO Reno 12 series
description: Oppo Reno 12 series will feature a 6.7-inch FHD+ 120Hz flexible AMOLED display. Oppo has also confirmed the “Quad-Micro Curved Infinite View” design for the display, which the company claims, possesses minimal side bezels to achieve a remarkable 93.5 per cent screen-to-body ratio

name: MacBook Pro 16-inch
description: The MacBook Pro 16-inch features an M1 Pro chip, 16GB RAM, 1TB SSD, and a stunning Retina display. Ideal for professionals seeking high performance.

name: Sony WH-1000XM4
description: Sony WH-1000XM4 wireless noise-canceling headphones offer superior sound quality and comfort, with up to 30 hours of battery life.

name: Nike Air Zoom Pegasus 39
description: Nike Air Zoom Pegasus 39 offers a comfortable and responsive ride with lightweight cushioning, making it perfect for runners of all levels.
